    <note>Xiang(2) Zongdan [710] Minzhong's [705] great grandson, Zongdao's [711] younger brother, Gun's [707] grandfather. Brother of one of Zhao(1) Shenzong's [9006] empresses. Same generational name as Zongzhe [708] and Zongru [709]. He once held a post in Zhenjiang and his son, Zixin [3358], moved to Tantu (modern Zhenjiang, the only county address of a Xiang(2) jinshi). XCB, 231.12a, 331.1b, 332.2a, 10a, 413.6a; Guangdong TZ, 15.3a; SHY:ZG, 66.21b. CBD, 1, 635.</note>
